        {
          "field": "description",
          "fieldtype": "jira",
          "fieldId": "description",
          "from": null,
          "fromString": "This will foucs on updating the task tree currently triggering off the File Info Object through the Foundation AI / WCB Mail process. The main change here is that we added a subcategory to the Document Type EC-88. We need to now account for different tasks that will trigger dependent on the sub-type. \n\nWe will be reorganizing this piece of the flow to account for the below \n\n!image-20251024-150216.png|width=671,alt=\"image-20251024-150216.png\"!\n\n\n\n# EC-88 / PON\n#* If Related Matter_WCB Number is blank, update value from file\n#* Update Related Matter_WCB_Retainer_Status__c\n# EC-88 / Fee App\n#* Create Task \n#* Assign Task to WC Attorney Queue\n#* Set Due Date on task to TODAY\n# EC-88 / NOS or Review\n#* Create Task \n#* Assign Task to Paralegal\n#* Set Due Date on task to TODAY",
          "to": null,
          "toString": "This will foucs on updating the task tree currently triggering off the File Info Object through the Foundation AI / WCB Mail process. The main change here is that we added a subcategory to the Document Type EC-88. We need to now account for different tasks that will trigger dependent on the sub-type. \n\nWe will be reorganizing this piece of the File Info After Save flow to account for the below \n\n!image-20251024-150216.png|width=671,alt=\"image-20251024-150216.png\"!\n\n\n\n# EC-88 / PON (compare to Notice of Assembly automation)\n#* If Related Matter_WCB Number is blank, update WC Number from file info object (WCB#)\n#* If Related Matter_WCB_Retainer_Status__c != On Notice, update to “On Notice”\n# EC-88 / FeeAPP\n#* Create Task id a04TV000007ZCQTYA4\n#* *Override Subject: “AT01: Review EC-88 - Fee App”*\n#* Assign Task to WC Attorney Queue\n#* Set Due Date on task to TODAY\n# EC-88 / NOS\n#* Create Task id a04TV000007ZCQTYA4\n#* *Override Subject: PL05: Review EC-88 - Notice of Sub*\n#* Assign Task to Paralegal\n#* Set Due Date on task to TODAY\n# EC-88 / Review\n#* If Matter_Case Stage/Active Stage = Settlement OR Permenancy\n#*# Create Task id a04TV000007ZCQTYA4\n#*# Assign Task to Settlement Coordinator\n#*# Set Due Date on task to TODAY\n#* Else\n#*# Create Task id a04TV000007ZCQTYA4\n#*# Assign Task to Paralegal\n#*# Set Due Date on task to TODAY\n# EC-88 blank/null sub type (just in case)\n## Same logic as EC-88/Review"
        }
      ]
    },
